Currently you cannot do this if someone is in melee with you. <P> Misses are currently auto giving interrupts. Thus not allowing you to chain ccast because of the 3+ secs to wait to cast after being interrupted.<P> However if you where to cast the amnesia spell on a bunch of tanks that are on your friend it "should" interrupt this swings (thus making it a miss).
