<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
It um... well... it.... uh.,........ it makes pretty sparkles on their heads. And that is about it.<P>I am still fighting to get it to remove targetting, at least then it would be useful. all i do with it against melee now is use it ass a shock/scare tactic. If an enemy force is edging up, the melees try to get just outide of range. this allows them to be a marker for their archers who use them as a gauge of distance sometimes.<P>I inch in and spam Amnesia and make sparkles all over the place. Since it is AE this will catch any rogue types near them also, and the AE can take it BYOND your range. So if they are right at 2300, your spells AE will go a full 3 to 6 paces beyond them and interrupt those archers and casters behind and around them also.<P>Doesn't do much, but surprises them. they usually back up a bit, thinking if that can hit them, something else could hit them also.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
