I Definately agree with you B! It never fails to drive off a large force inching their way up to you. <P>People would call me crazy because I would be up in front of our force, spaming AE amnesia, slowly inching Mids/Hibs back to their PK's. <P>It wouldn't be long till they would send in their Assassins for suicide missions (yellow con assassins could never one shot me at lvl 35, so by the time they wack me they were dead). With this tactic alone I can have hours of fun (err ok maybe not hours... but you get the idea).<P>Also, by spamming Amnesia sometimes you can get a feel for how bold the apposing side is. Every once in a while I was able to inch up close enough to SPRINT/QC AE MEZ.  BAM! I then ran back to the Albs yelling, "THEY ARE AE MEZED ATTACK!"... lol it has worked several of times. Way fun!! <P>And that is, kind of the reason, why I rolled up another Sorcerer. Because I know I can get another Sorcerer up to 35 faster than I can get my 35 to 50 =p<P><BR>Riz...
